Name: Type
Description: Indicates value type as "GreaterThan", LessThan", "Equal", "GreaterThanOrEqual", "LessThanOrEqual", or "NotEqual".
Enumeration: GreaterThan LessThan Equal GreaterThanOrEqual LessThanOrEqual NotEqual

Name: ValueIsBlank
Description: Set to "true" if the value of the conditional variable is blank.
